{"id":849,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":849,"title":"Ezekiel 21","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 21"],[".studySummary",["i","Both the righteous and the wicked in Jerusalem will be slain—Babylon will draw a sharp and bright sword against Israel and will prevail."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.1","order":"02.27.021.56475"},["b","1"],"And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.2","order":"02.27.021.56476"},["b","2"],"Son of man, set thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"face"],"toward Jerusalem, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"drop",["i","thy word"],"toward"],"the holy places, and prophesy against the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"land of Israel"],","],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.3","order":"02.27.021.56477"},["b","3"],"And say to the land of Israel, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Behold, I",["i","am"],"against thee, and will draw forth my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sword"],"out of his sheath, and will cut off from thee the righteous and the wicked."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.4","order":"02.27.021.56478"},["b","4"],"Seeing then that I will cut off from thee the righteous and the wicked, therefore shall my sword go forth out of his sheath against all flesh from the south to the north:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.5","order":"02.27.021.56479"},["b","5"],"That all flesh may know that I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have drawn forth my sword out of his sheath: it shall not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"return"],"any more."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.6","order":"02.27.021.56480"},["b","6"],"Sigh therefore, thou son of man, with the breaking of",["i","thy"],"loins; and with bitterness sigh before their eyes."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.7","order":"02.27.021.56481"},["b","7"],"And it shall be, when they say unto thee, Wherefore sighest thou? that thou shalt answer, For the tidings; because it cometh: and every heart shall melt, and all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"hands"],"shall be feeble, and every spirit shall faint, and all knees shall be weak",["i","as"],"water: behold, it cometh, and shall be brought to pass, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.8","order":"02.27.021.56482"},["b","8"],"¶Again the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.9","order":"02.27.021.56483"},["b","9"],"Son of man, prophesy, and say, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Say, A sword, a sword is sharpened, and also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"furbished"],":"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.10","order":"02.27.021.56484"},["b","10"],"It is sharpened to make a sore slaughter; it is furbished that it may glitter: should we then make mirth? it contemneth the rod of my son,",["i","as"],"every tree."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.11","order":"02.27.021.56485"},["b","11"],"And he hath given it to be furbished, that it may be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"handled"],": this sword is sharpened, and it is furbished, to give it into the hand of the slayer."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.12","order":"02.27.021.56486"},["b","12"],"Cry and howl, son of man: for it shall be upon my people, it",["i","shall be"],"upon all the princes of Israel: terrors by reason of the sword shall be upon my people: smite therefore upon",["i","thy"],"thigh."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.13","order":"02.27.021.56487"},["b","13"],"Because",["i","it is"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"trial"],", and what if",["i","the sword"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"contemn"],"even the rod? it shall be no",["i","more,"],"saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.14","order":"02.27.021.56488"},["b","14"],"Thou therefore, son of man, prophesy, and smite",["i","thine"],"hands together, and let the sword be doubled the third time, the sword of the slain: it",["i","is"],"the sword of the great",["i","men that are"],"slain, which entereth into their privy chambers."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.15","order":"02.27.021.56489"},["b","15"],"I have set the point of the sword against all their gates, that",["i","their"],"heart may faint, and",["i","their"],"ruins be multiplied: ah!",["i","it is"],"made bright,",["i","it is"],"wrapped up for the slaughter."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.16","order":"02.27.021.56490"},["b","16"],"Go thee one way or other,",["i","either"],"on the right hand,",["i","or"],"on the left, whithersoever thy face",["i","is"],"set."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.17","order":"02.27.021.56491"},["b","17"],"I will also smite mine hands together, and I will cause my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"fury"],"to rest: I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have said",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.18","order":"02.27.021.56492"},["b","18"],"¶The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me again, saying,"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.19","order":"02.27.021.56493"},["b","19"],"Also, thou son of man, appoint thee two ways, that the sword of the king of Babylon may come: both twain shall come forth out of one land: and choose thou a place, choose",["i","it"],"at the head of the way to the city."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.20","order":"02.27.021.56494"},["b","20"],"Appoint a way, that the sword may come to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Rabbath"],"of the Ammonites, and to Judah in Jerusalem the defenced."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.21","order":"02.27.021.56495"},["b","21"],"For the king of Babylon stood at the parting of the way, at the head of the two ways, to use divination: he made",["i","his"],"arrows bright, he consulted with images, he looked in the liver."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.22","order":"02.27.021.56496"},["b","22"],"At his right hand was the divination for Jerusalem, to appoint captains, to open the mouth in the slaughter, to lift up the voice with shouting, to appoint",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"battering"]],"rams against the gates, to cast",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"a mount"],",",["i","and"],"to build",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"a fort"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.23","order":"02.27.021.56497"},["b","23"],"And it shall be unto them as a false divination in their sight, to them that have sworn oaths: but he will call to remembrance the iniquity, that they may be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"taken"],"."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.24","order":"02.27.021.56498"},["b","24"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Because ye have made your iniquity to be remembered, in that your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"transgressions"],"are discovered, so that in all your doings your sins do appear; because,",["i","I say,"],"that ye are come to remembrance, ye shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"taken with the hand"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.25","order":"02.27.021.56499"},["b","25"],"¶And thou, profane",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"wicked"],"prince of Israel, whose",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"day"],"is come, when iniquity",["i","shall have"],"an end,"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.26","order":"02.27.021.56500"},["b","26"],"Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Remove the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"diadem"],", and take off the crown: this",["i","shall"],"not",["i","be"],"the same: exalt",["i","him that is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"low"],", and abase",["i","him that is"],"high."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.27","order":"02.27.021.56501"},["b","27"],"I will overturn, overturn, overturn, it: and it shall be no",["i","more,"],"until he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"come"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"whose"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"right"],"it is; and I will give it",["i","him."]],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.28","order":"02.27.021.56502"},["b","28"],"¶And thou, son of man, prophesy and say, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"concerning the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Ammonites"],", and concerning their reproach; even say thou, The sword, the sword",["i","is"],"drawn: for the slaughter",["i","it is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"furbished"],", to consume because of the glittering:"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.29","order":"02.27.021.56503"},["b","29"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"Whiles"],"they see vanity unto thee, whiles they divine a lie unto thee, to bring thee upon the necks of",["i","them that are"],"slain, of the wicked, whose day is come, when their iniquity",["i","shall have"],"an end."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.30","order":"02.27.021.56504"},["b","30"],"Shall I cause",["i","it"],"to return into his sheath? I will judge thee in the place where thou wast created, in the land of thy nativity."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.31","order":"02.27.021.56505"},["b","31"],"And I will pour out mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"indignation"],"upon thee, I will blow against thee in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"fire"],"of my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_31c"},"wrath"],", and deliver thee into the hand of brutish men,",["i","and"],"skilful to destroy."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.32","order":"02.27.021.56506"},["b","32"],"Thou shalt be for fuel to the fire; thy blood shall be in the midst of the land; thou shalt be no",["i","more"],"remembered: for I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have spoken",["i","it."]]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.2a","order":"02.27.021.56507"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.46"},"Ezek. 20:46"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.2b","order":"02.27.021.56509"},["b","2b"],["span.small","OR"],"preach against."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.2c","order":"02.27.021.56511"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-land-of"},"TG Israel, Land of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.3a","order":"02.27.021.56513"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.13"},"D&C 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.5a","order":"02.27.021.56515"},["b","5a"],["span.small","IE"],"be sheathed."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.7a","order":"02.27.021.56517"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.17"},"Ezek. 7:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.9a","order":"02.27.021.56519"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"polished."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.11a","order":"02.27.021.56521"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"seized by hand."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.13a","order":"02.27.021.56523"},["b","13a"],["span.small","OR"],"time of testing."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.13b","order":"02.27.021.56525"},["b","13b"],["span.small","HEB"],"reject."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.17a","order":"02.27.021.56527"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.13"},"Ezek. 5:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.21"},"3 Ne. 21:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.20a","order":"02.27.021.56529"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.2"},"Jer. 49:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.5.4-5"},"Ezek. 25:5 (4–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.14"},"Amos 1:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.22a","order":"02.27.021.56531"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2"},"Ezek. 4:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.22b","order":"02.27.021.56533"},["b","22b"],["span.small","OR"],"siege mounds."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.22c","order":"02.27.021.56535"},["b","22c"],["span.small","OR"],"siegeworks."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.23a","order":"02.27.021.56537"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/17.20.20,24"},"Ezek. 17:20 (20, 24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.24a","order":"02.27.021.56539"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.9"},"D&C 3:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.24b","order":"02.27.021.56541"},["b","24b"],["span.small","IE"],"captured."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.25a","order":"02.27.021.56543"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/36.12.12-13"},"2 Chr. 36:12 (12–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.25b","order":"02.27.021.56545"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.3"},"Ezek. 22:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.26a","order":"02.27.021.56547"},["b","26a"],["span.small","HEB"],"headdress or miter."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.26b","order":"02.27.021.56549"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.52"},"Luke 1:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.27a","order":"02.27.021.56551"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.27b","order":"02.27.021.56553"},["b","27b"],"The Hebrew word",["span.translit",["span.emphasis","shiloh"]],"may be a short form of",["span.translit",["span.emphasis","asher-lo,"]],"which can be rendered “whose right it is.”"],["div",{"id":"27c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.27c","order":"02.27.021.56555"},["b","27c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.10"},"Gen. 49:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.28a","order":"02.27.021.56557"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.2.1-2"},"Jer. 49:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.28b","order":"02.27.021.56559"},["b","28b"],["span.small","OR"],"polished."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.29a","order":"02.27.021.56561"},["b","29a"],["span.small","IE"],"While they see false visions for you."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.31a","order":"02.27.021.56563"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.31b","order":"02.27.021.56565"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.21.20-21"},"Ezek. 22:21 (20–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"31c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.31c","order":"02.27.021.56567"},["b","31c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.26"},"D&C 43:26"],"."]]}
